snippet.title: Rack and Slay [Reveal Trailer]
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2311990/Rack_and_Slay/

The rogue-like dungeon crawler where you're a billiard ball! Push monster balls into holes or traps in randomly generated levels. Draft from a large variety of stackable items with game-changing effects. Find combos to build your own synergies and customize your playstyle. Rack and Slay!
